{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"eaad462a45","title":"转发中南军区秋季情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8522fc0180","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":29,"articleId":"eaad462a45"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"623e08d6bc","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"贺，指贺龙，当时任中国人民解放军西南军区司令员。邓，指邓小平，当时任中国人民解放军西南军区政治委员。"},{"id":"08d7654e2c","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张，指张宗逊，当时任中国人民解放军西北军区副司令员。廿，指甘泗淇，当时任中国人民解放军西北军区副政治委员兼政治部主任。"},{"id":"5d1ac9784f","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指邓子恢等1950年12月24日关于中南区剩汇情况给毛泽东和军委的报告中总结的剩经验，主要是：1.在剩部署上严格掌握重点进、首先集中兵力歼灭大股徒的方针；2.在作战上采用奔袭、包围动作，黑夜雨天出动，出敌不意，予以歼灭；3.执行宽大与镇压相结合的方针，纠正宽大无边的错误；4.在军事进则的同时，吸收各界人士对汇徒展开劝降，进行瓦解和争取。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d3d943d4fb","type":"title","text":"转发中南军区秋李剃能情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45"},{"id":"623e08d6bc","type":"paragraph","text":"陈、张，贺、郑问，张、甘以：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45"},{"id":"08d7654e2c","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将中南军区秋季期经验马发给你们参考，请加研究，这些经验是很有用的","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45"},{"id":"5d1ac9784f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45"},{"id":"8d62327aeb","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月廿九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45"},{"id":"cdb8c11250","type":"paragraph","text":"口1陈，指陈毅，当时任中国人民解放军华东军区司令员。张，指张震，当时任中国人民解放军华东军区参谋长。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45"}],"page":{"id":"017864da84","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"eaad462a45","start":472,"end":472}}}},"__N_SSG":true}